-- Triveni Engineering Falls in Mumbai Trading After Posting Quarterly Loss
-- Hari Govind
-- 2010-07-20T03:33:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/triveni-engineering-falls-in-mumbai-trading-after-posting-quarterly-loss.html

          
          
             Triveni Engineering & Industries
Ltd. fell as much as 5.5 percent in Mumbai trading after posting
a loss in the third quarter.  
 The shares dropped 4.2 percent to 98.65 rupees as of 9:01
a.m. local time. The company had a loss of of 142.3 million
rupees in the three months ended June 30, compared with a net
income of 398.1 million rupees a year earlier, according to a
statement sent to the Bombay Stock Exchange yesterday.  
          
          


  


        